-- Lehman Brothers Buys $1.8 Billion of Claims on Itself From JPMorgan
-- Linda Sandler
-- 2010-07-06T21:29:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-06/lehman-brothers-buys-1-8-billion-of-claims-on-itself-from-jpmorgan.html

          
          
             Lehman Brothers Holdings Inc. bought
more than $1.8 billion in claims on itself from  JPMorgan Chase &
Co. , according to court filings today. The transfers were part
of a March agreement whereby JPMorgan will return $9 billion in
illiquid securities and real estate, taking cash and collateral
from Lehman, according to filings.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
